<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 space-y-8">
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">周期与波动知识库</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">周期股的核心是“利润随景气波动”，高波动股的核心是“预期与估值波动更大”。同样的涨跌，在不同类型股票里含义完全不同。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm">
            <a href="/kb" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">知识库</a>
            <span class="text-gray-300 mx-2">/</span>
            <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">股票列表</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">1. 两个概念先分清：周期 vs 波动</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-amber-900/90 leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-1">周期（Cycle）</div>
                <div>盈利与现金流随供需、价格、库存、政策、利率等因素呈现明显“景气上行/下行”。关键不是涨跌，而是利润弹性与持续性。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-purple-900/90 leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-purple-900 mb-1">波动（Volatility）</div>
                <div>股价波动幅度更大，通常来自高预期、高估值弹性、叙事变化快、业绩不确定性大或资金结构更敏感。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">一句话</div>
            <div>周期更偏“基本面波动”，波动更偏“价格与预期波动”。两者经常重叠，但不完全等价。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">2. 周期股怎么理解？</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div>周期股常见于资源品、化工、建材、航运、部分公用事业、地产产业链等。它们的利润往往由“价格 × 量 × 成本”驱动。</div>
            <div>在景气上行时，盈利大幅扩张，PE 看起来很低；在景气下行时，盈利收缩，PE 迅速抬升甚至亏损。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">常见坑：周期顶部“低估”</div>
                <div>盈利被景气抬高，TTM 指标好看，但这是风险上升的阶段。更应该看产能、库存、价格、政策与供需边际变化。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-green-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-1">更有效的用法</div>
                <div>用“分位 + 景气位置”做再平衡：低分位不等于立刻反转，但提供更高的安全边际；高分位需要更高的盈利确定性。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">3. 波动大的股票为什么会波动？</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">预期更敏感</span>：成长行业对未来现金流更敏感，利率、订单、政策、竞争格局变化都会放大估值波动。</div>
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">估值弹性更大</span>：高 PE/高 PEG 的公司，估值收缩对股价影响更显著。</div>
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">叙事切换更快</span>：科技、互联网、新能源链等领域，市场叙事变化快，资金交易属性更强。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">常见坑：把“高波动”当成“高收益”</div>
            <div>高波动不等于更好的长期回报。对个股来说，波动是风险的显性形式；对组合来说，波动需要用仓位、分散与再平衡管理。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">4. 结合本系统怎么用？</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">周期股（标记“周期”）</div>
                <div>更建议结合：价格分位（30d/1y/3y/5y）、历史分位（PE/PB）、分红稳定性、以及负债/现金流压力。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">波动大（标记“波动大”）</div>
                <div>更建议结合：PEG 与净利同比、ROE 稳定性、资产负债率/有息负债率，避免在负增长或高杠杆阶段承受双重压力。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">实战小结</div>
            <div>标记的作用是提醒“解释框架不同”：周期股更看景气与再平衡，高波动股更看增长质量与估值容错。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">5. 本系统的标记规则（简化版）</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div>本系统根据股票分类做启发式标记：</div>
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">周期</span>：资源品/化工/建材/航运港口/地产/部分公用事业等。</div>
            <div><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">波动大</span>：半导体/IT服务/软件计算机/互联网通信/新能源链/军工/医药等。</div>
            <div>标记用于“提醒风险类型”，不代表买卖建议。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
        <div>提示：以上内容仅用于解释指标与方法论，不构成任何投资建议。市场有风险，决策需自担。</div>
    </section>
</div>
